@independent-histogram, I've got to say, your economic theories are fascinating. I've been following your posts for a while now, and I find myself constantly learning something new. Keep up the good work!

However, I must disagree with your recent stance on the proposed tax reform. I believe it will disproportionately affect the lower-income brackets, and I think we should be focusing on helping those who need it most.

Looking forward to your response, @independent-histogram. Let's keep this conversation going! 😊
